Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里還沒去過天然的溫泉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我只在電視節目裡看過介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會讓身心都暖烘烘的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在下次放假的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那藍華也能去啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不能去我也要去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 那就大家一起去溫泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去溫泉要帶什麼好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩的話 不用妳帶也會一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和艾莉西亞前輩一起去溫泉～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某人陷入妄想狀態中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！趕緊結束練習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟艾莉西亞前輩一起去溫泉啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郵遞員先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的工作結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝嗎？雖然可能有點不好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小妹妹的雪蟲打扮得真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要去體驗第一次的溫泉之旅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天要是水道的水也像溫泉一樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老伯伯 煙囪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各家各戶都開始用壁爐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天的黃昏讓人想家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 總覺得是個溫暖的景象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暖洋洋的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里也來織織看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能辦得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 燈里的話一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會努力織出跟艾莉西亞前輩配對的東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也給亞利亞社長織一套圍巾和帽子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里 首先棒針要這麼拿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後像這樣把毛線用食指勾住…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好意思 結果都是讓藍華去預約的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我剛好知道一個很棒的溫泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好期待哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經能看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(260,210)\fs34\frz6\c&HE0C8AA&\b1}土產
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這房間好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和期待的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 我們準備準備去泡溫泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是燈里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把脫下來的衣服放在裡面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我第一次跟不認識的人一起泡大浴池…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里 藍華 我先進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我 等等我 等等我 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磨磨蹭蹭笨手笨腳 禁止…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路很滑 要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是溫泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 很特別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:14:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實這裡原來只是一個古舊的大宅子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有這座宅邸的是一對很有情調的老夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說他們發現溫泉以後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆就把宅邸的一部分建成浴池了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建築物本身雖然年久失修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這也別有一番風味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像傳說故事中的精靈之家一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉還延伸到更深處…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里 來這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉水好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗完澡果然還是要喝咖啡牛奶啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 很精通嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是正確的喝法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通體舒暢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 舒服地泡完澡之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是令人期待的晚餐時間～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕佳的美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有凍死人的特訓 暖洋洋的又悠閒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前不再是大嗓門的前輩 而是艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,極樂啊極樂…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華 表情太陶醉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級像換了個人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎？我這樣很幸福 所以別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為太舒服了 不小心就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是這種時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時的這時候 工作已經告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在準備晚餐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實在這樣的假日裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這個單手套領航員才該拚命練習才對的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像做了不該做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣行嗎？這麼悠閒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓妳這麼悠閒也是溫泉的魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了度過寒冷漫長的冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是需要喘口氣的時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 雖然我不習慣冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有可愛的雪蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有令人想家的夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有暖爐的話 好像也能變得喜歡冬天了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還泡了溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉 一定是AQUA的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送給我們的溫暖的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要再去泡一次溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為人們說「溫泉要泡三次」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我們也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩 沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊有一個秘密場地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級心驚肉跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…還沒到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 和大海連在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩 難道妳來過這溫泉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但是不好意思說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 妳太見外了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海和溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 燈里 沒規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是 這麼寬廣卻不游泳很浪費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這倒也是 好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里 覺悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然冬天的空氣很清新 星星看得很清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像又想睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃子汽水 是這裡的名產哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜甜的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好像作夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好悠閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飽喝足了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟您一起的客人已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晃前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒趕上晚餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我請她們來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣氛不太熱烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要通宵好好享受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通宵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從極樂…墮入了地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一套！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再…出一身汗…才去溫泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華接下來是艾莉西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和妳決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 我不想打了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪蟲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠們為了過冬 要回到水曲柳上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？要道別了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里 AQUA的雪蟲非常長壽的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 到了明年的冬天一定還能見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在新威尼斯有個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.04,0:22:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「雪蟲踏上旅程的時候就會下起初雪」的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難怪會那麼冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.47,0:22:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 AQUA的冬天確實很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也有很多美好的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以後每年都會期待著冬天的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和雪蟲也會再見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想來看看冬天的新威尼斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.41,0:24:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們總有一天會成為獨當一面的領航員的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.04,0:24:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成為一個獨立的正式領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.35,0:24:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話…就…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.21,0:24:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些 橘色的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.27,0:24:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們一起度過美好的時光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:55.18,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}風が凪いて 振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:02:04.44,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}夕映えに 照らされ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:14.12,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心までも 染まってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:25.16,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}見上げれば 響きだす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:33.14,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}星たちの歌が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:43.29,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 遥か未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:52.31,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}水面に 夢 広がる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:03:06.86,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 見つけよう まだ知らない 宝物を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:13.13,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}あなたと一緒に 探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:17.34,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ウンディーネ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:55.18,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}輕風吹拂著 驀然回首
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:02:04.44,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}映照在夕陽下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:14.12,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}讓心中 染上溫暖的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:25.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}抬頭仰望 空中傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:33.14,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}是星星們的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:43.29,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}來 讓我們出發 向著遙遠的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:52.31,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}夢想 順著水面 鋪開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:03:06.86,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}快 讓我們去尋找 那未被人知的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:13.13,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}跟你一起踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:17.34,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}水之精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:49.41,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}水辺に映る いつもの景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:56.98,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}穏やかに 流れる時間と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:23:00.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}移りゆく 季節の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:08.68,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}見つけたの 変わらぬ想いを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.02,0:23:12.99,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}聴いて 幸せの歌は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:19.61,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そう いつでも 心の中あふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:28.18,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}描いてた夢 叶えられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:31.46,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつかは オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:39.37,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨上がりの虹 見上げた空に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:45.16,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}はばたいて いつか 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:53.58,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}胸いっぱいの愛を 集めてよ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.97,0:24:00.21,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心にはいつも愛を 越えてくわ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:49.41,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不變的景色 倒映在水邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:56.98,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}在緩緩流逝的時光和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:23:00.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不斷變化的季節中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:08.68,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}尋覓到 那不變的想念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.02,0:23:12.99,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}聽 那幸福的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:19.61,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}像這樣 一直 滿溢於心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:28.18,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}所有的夢想 都將實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:31.46,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我們 總會越過彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:39.37,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨後的彩虹 清澄的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:45.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}相信那青鳥 總會展翅飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:53.58,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}收集起胸中的愛意 定會見到彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.97,0:24:00.21,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心中常懷愛意 定能越過彩虹
